                    <h1>
                        In Loving Memory of Aerith Gainsborough
                    </h1>
                    <p>Today is a sad day.  The world lost an amazing, bright young woman named Aerith Gainsborough.</p>
                    <p>Aerith was not only a valued customer at Seventh Heaven, but also a dear friend of ours.  She was 
                        one of the kindest, most cheerful people I had ever known in my life.  She was an amazing friend, 
                        and just so full of life, but tragically, her life was cut short by Sephiroth after he impaled her 
                        with his infamous sword known as the Masamune.</p>
                    <p>A private funeral service was held for Aerith at the Forgotten City.  She will be dearly missed, 
                        but never forgotten.</p>
                    <p>Sephiroth will not get away with this.  We are doing everything we can to bring him to justice and
                        make sure he can never harm another innocent person ever again.</p>
